{"tid":2350981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2020之後我睇到香港流行文化嘅希望","createTime":"2021-01-02T20:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T09:39:36.000Z","uid":372196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4b4b1d4d360e5946651da005319391af87b414","tid":2350981,"uid":372196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T20:28:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">2020年，</span></strong></span><br />\n因為疫情，戲院冇乜外國戲，<br />\n我哋有<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">幻愛、叔叔、金都、死因冇可疑</span></span></strong><br />\n因為疫情，坐喺屋企嘅時間多咗，睇多咗電視，<br />\n我哋唔再睇TVB，我哋睇<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">暖男爸爸、男排女將、全民造星</span></span></strong><br />\n因為疫情，我哋多咗時間，多咗聽歌，<br />\n我哋終於知嗰個<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">乜水叫柳應廷、開始聽開始係咁飄嘅Ian、偶像派嘅姜濤、突然冒出嘅實力派林家謙、捱咗好多年嘅馮允謙、天生二品嘅陳凱泳⋯</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢度唔能夠盡列，<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"violet\">希望2021，係香港流行文化重新起步嘅里程碑！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">叱吒</span></span>就係2021一個好嘅好開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家不妨係下面推介唔同Made in HK 嘅短片、歌曲、電影、劇集等等，大家一齊J<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bae649afdc86ad35b597da4e585fa5c1fd4d35d","tid":2350981,"uid":372196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T20:28:53.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573df242d6969863f997b2612a6982175196c23c","tid":2350981,"uid":367123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T20:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac